points, all their airfields, all their bases, all

28:57.566 --> 29:04.015
their supply lines. you know, all the 
headquarters and communication sites. So they

29:07.370 --> 29:08.372
were isolated down there. Then the right time 
came, and we surrounded them, and then we went in

29:09.894 --> 29:14.321
and went in for their army and beat them. We had to 
defeat their army. That was just the opposite.

