them. You just stop. Then they sit there. They 
regroup. They retrain. They resupply. And when

29:51.386 --> 29:54.370
the timing's right, they come across again. In the 
meantime, they're inflicting harassment

29:54.873 --> 30:08.188
actions all the time through artillery or having 
